🎉 Happy Birthday to the Queen of Our Castle 👑
My wife, my best friend, the love of my life…
…and also the CEO of Eye Rolls, Master of Multitasking, and the only person who can look like a diva while surviving on 3 hours of sleep and baby snacks.

From being the most glamorous partner to the most patient, loving mama, you do it all — and somehow make it look easy (while I panic if the Wi-Fi goes down 😅).

You are our calm, our chaos, our laughter, and our light.

Siyana and I hit the jackpot — and even though you say “I’m fine” when you’re clearly not…
We know you carry the weight of this world with grace, grit, and a little bit of glitter ✨

Today we celebrate YOU — not just for who you are to us, but for the amazing woman you are to the world.
We love you more than clean diapers and coffee… and that’s saying A LOT. ❤️

#HappyBirthdayAvni #QueenOfOurHearts #MomGoals #DivaModeOn #FamilyFirst #wifeyforlifey

Happy Birthday to my wife, my best friend, and the queen of our little chaos 👑
A total diva with the kindest heart, the loudest laugh, and the softest hugs.
Siyana and I are the luckiest — even if you boss us around 98% of the time 😅
Love you more than sleep and silence (which you’ve stolen since becoming a mom 😂).
Grateful for you, every single day ❤️

One whole year of our sweet Siyana. Watching her grow has been the most beautiful journey—each smile, step, and milestone fills our hearts with endless love and pride. She’s growing so fast, and we’re soaking in every moment. Mommy and Daddy love you more than words can say, baby girl—you truly are our whole world.

Thank you to all our family and friends who celebrated this special day with us. Your love and presence made her first birthday even more magical!
